   Open-source Javascript-based Antelope smart contract testing framework,
   created by GenerEOS (https://genereos.io) with funding from the
   EOS Network Foundation (https://eosnetwork.com). Provided Docker-based
   Leap node orchestration, snapshot-based chain initialization for EOS,
   WAX, and TELOS networks, libfaketime-based chain time manipulation,
   table data seeding via custom WASM actions, and parallel test execution
   via Jest workers with multi-architecture (ARM/AMD64) support.
